download java 5.0 > download jdk 6u1 > download hamachi > choose a source (pimpscape reccomended from me) > download it > go to documents > right click it and extract to desktop > double click the folder on the desktop > scroll down and double click on compiler > choose the option to compile > then exit out and click run server.

there you go.
